final_question: On Tuesday , Rehmat Ullah wants to exercise for twice the amount of time he did on Monday and Sunday combined . On Sunday he exercised for 23 minutes . On Monday he exercised for 16 minutes . How many minutes does he have to exercise on Tuesday to reach his goal ?
